LEGEND:
* = To do
? = Maybe
I = in progress
T = Needs testing
W = waiting on other work
X = Done

X Do something neat with the appicon, like NeXT's clock (wmCalClock?)
? UNIX module, to set things in Workspace
* Colors module
X Date/Time module
I Fonts module
* Localization (setting preferred language(s))
* Mouse module (accel speed, double-click delay, menu button)
* Services module, to deactivate/activate services
* User Interface module (InterfaceStyle stuff, Open/Save panels, ...)
* Display module, containing screen-blanking and monitor gamma controls.
